rows.label: qst701805_msg0001
rows.name:
Three Golden Sand Cocoons,
three Cotton Branches...

rows.label: qst701805_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh, and two Bladed Holly twigs.
I think that was it...?

rows.label: qst701805_msg0003
rows.name:
I've got no idea why we need those
things but if Kasumi-san say we need
them then they must be important.

rows.label: qst701805_msg0004
rows.name:
And from what Kasumi said,
those Golden Sand Cocoons
are the rarest ones.

rows.label: qst701805_msg0005
rows.name:
They're made by bugs that only live in
the Streamsand Corridor, if I remember
Adel-sama's words correctly...

rows.label: qst701805_msg0006
rows.name:
Sorry for the bother. But I've gotta
find a way to conquer needlework
at any cost.

rows.label: qst701805_msg0007
rows.name:
I'll do as Kasumi-san tells me and there's
no way I'm quitting. So please help me
out here and I promise to try my best!
